I believe the MOB must be within a 350 range of your before it will find enemy targets to aggro on. I have already heard of casting on a yellow, and a nearby yellow comes also.... but as soon as they are within the 350 range, the confused tries to attack the other one that is brought.<P>Not sure if this kicks in a group MOB bonus for XP or not, but it certainly changes the dynamic of this spell.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
